---
title: Backyard Bacon-Ranch Potato Salad Serves 2 | with Cheddar Cheese and Green Onions
description: This creamy, dreamy potato salad is stuffed to the brim with crowd-pleasing cheddar cheese, herby green onions and the smoky flavour of crisp bacon. It's easy to throw together and will go great with whatever you're grilling up!
